description:
MindCrack FTB is a modded Minecraft server Guude has setup for the MindCrackers. It is a private (whitelisted) server. We are currently not accepting applications.

Today we start designing the teleport room to handle player respawning for the PVP map. There are 7 spawn points on the map, 3 for Node A, 1 for Node B, and 3 for Node C. Ideally we want to randomize which spawn points players start at, and only if their team owns that spawn point and no other players are near it.

FTB Mod Pack Info: http://feed-the-beast.com/
MindCrack: http://www.youtube.com/user/MindCrackNetwork
